.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, mexican
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, pink
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, skateboard
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the goat is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | puzzles    |
| Pet           | goldfish     | goat |
| Nationality   | mexican    | japanese   |
| Color         | orange | pink   |
| Transport     | helicopter | skateboard |

