.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi
2 different games are played: snooker, billiard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, nigerian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Food          | kiwi     | cranberry     |
| Game   | snooker   | billiard        |
| Flower   | aconite      | amaryllis         |
| Nationality   | nigerian | italian       |
| Sport         | cycling  | skateboarding |

